{"tid":897754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「愛情是一種最精良、最狡猾、也最有效的社會壓迫工具。」","createTime":"2018-11-11T07:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T07:59:35.000Z","uid":145472,"like":52,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1234d3bd0bd00307985791a5f80690846c9290a","tid":897754,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"德國電影大師法斯賓達 (Rainer Werner Fassbinder) 講過︰<br />\n「愛情是一種最精良、最狡猾、也最有效的社會壓迫工具。」<br />\n<br />\n (Love seems to me the best, most sneaky and effective instrument of social oppression)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹聽完 Juno 首《困獸.28》好有感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n幾多人為咗養女朋友同養家，被迫做好多自己唔想做嘅嘢，返一份唔想返但安定嘅工，一世咁就困住咗。<br />\n<br />\n（毒撚唔該背熟呢句，人地話你無女朋友時，你話自己無欲則剛，唔想俾社會壓迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：無囡就無囡啦多多事實，死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e0df7d7b9e4ce3312717d4cc90080bc0218380","tid":897754,"uid":145472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：10<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：3<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b135ee35f4349adb38aed007eb5e638d6681e75","tid":897754,"uid":221386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"立場中肯 8/10 <br />\n宜舉例1-2句歌詞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1256ee274cd56cf065403ffc4d7c75c66b7e95","tid":897754,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"for man"},{"pid":"835ce297b425e7b9e9b1f4a5453d70b793e76799","tid":897754,"uid":145472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b135ee35f4349adb38aed007eb5e638d6681e75","tid":897754,"uid":221386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"立場中肯 8/10 <br />\n宜舉例1-2句歌詞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"成日話人「單身狗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n但夕爺呢首詞卻反稱被迫一齊嘅情侶為「被困的狗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n無錯，籠入面有安定有溫飽，<br />\n但狗始終係鍾意自由嘅動物，唔鍾意被困。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「恆久這樣地忠心親厚乖巧馴服 叫你我也很狗<br />\n誰亦沒惡意犯錯應忍受<br />\n......<br />\n你跟我就是那雙未慣溫飽的困獸<br />\n勒索彼此的溫柔 <br />\n寧願去吹吹風似  流浪狗」<br />\n<br />\n「鬥垮世俗後  結果是更不自由」<br />\n「你跟我侷在甕中漸變抑鬱走獸」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lZrg-UsdZkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlZrg-UsdZkE&d=nU4zFllnu80LzyJiqHEC%2BP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0d1afa1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lZrg-UsdZkE</a>"},{"pid":"f96ac8cbd802b22642d236b03b19c0f088454a61","tid":897754,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 26<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab69f35da59f33cc330a6e1069c5b1cdb17c28b6","tid":897754,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"974db09aaaf8d9b7c0ba45d79cd7c9f1dee88738","tid":897754,"uid":17492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:27:38.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n不過我有女你冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a537ac357fe9a9c2500f